tplinkStaticRouteMIB.name: tplinkStaticRouteMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

tplinkStaticRouteMIB.description: Private MIB for static route configuration.

tpStaticRouteConfigTable.name: tpStaticRouteConfigTable
tpStaticRouteConfigTable.description: A list of static route entries.Route is choosing a best way to trasmit the data from the source to the destination.Static route is a special route,it is set by the administrator,and it is not automatically changed along with the change of network topo, so the static route is most used in the net which is small and has a fixed topo with virtues of simple,efficient and reliable.

tpStaticRouteConfigEntry.name: tpStaticRouteConfigEntry
tpStaticRouteConfigEntry.description: The item can be added or removed .

tpStaticRouteItemDesIp.name: tpStaticRouteItemDesIp
tpStaticRouteItemDesIp.description: The ip Address of the packet should be arrived

tpStaticRouteItemNextIp.name: tpStaticRouteItemNextIp
tpStaticRouteItemNextIp.description: The next jump ip address which the packet would be sent to by the switch.

tpStaticRouteItemInterfaceName.name: tpStaticRouteItemInterfaceName
tpStaticRouteItemInterfaceName.description: The name of the VLAN interface.

tpStaticRouteItemStatus.name: tpStaticRouteItemStatus
tpStaticRouteItemStatus.description: The following values are states: these values may be used as follow: active(1),if the entry is being used. notInService(2),destory the entry. notReady(3),destory the entry. createAndGo(4),not being used createAndWait(5),creat a new entry destroy(6),destory the entry.
